at http://healthmap.org/r/0_fB.

According to WAHID's data, FMD is currently circulating in several
countries in southern Africa. The following links provide updated
summaries including maps and the respective serotype for each of those
countries:

Botswana (serotype SAT2)
http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=10548
Mozambique (serotype SAT2)
http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=9766
South Africa (serotype SAT1)
http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=10290
Zambia (serotype O)
http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=9970
Zimbabwe (serotype SAT2)
http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=event_summary&reportid=9365.

The apparent circulation of 3 different serotypes deserves
confirmation from a reference FMD laboratory. - Mod.AS]
